efi: Use PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO()

Fix ptr_ret.cocci warnings:

  drivers/firmware/efi/efi.c:610:8-14: WARNING: PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO can be used

Use PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO rather than if(IS_ERR(...)) + PTR_ERR

